OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FThe decision has reignited the debate
OL,7,Faround "sportswashing" in football,
OL,8,Fwith human rights groups raising
OL,9,Fconcerns over the country's record
OL,11,FWord by Jamel Smith, ITV News Producer
OL,13,FFifa's decision to select Saudi Arabia
OL,14,Fto host the 2034 World Cup has come
OL,15,Funder fire from human rights groups
OL,16,Fover the country's record on women's
OL,17,Frights, LGBT issues, executions and
OL,18,Ffree speech.
