OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FMichael Page, deputy Middle East and
OL,7,FNorth Africa director at Human Rights
OL,8,FWatch (HRW), recently warned that if
OL,9,FSaudi Arabia hosted the football event
OL,10,Fthere could be an "unimaginable human
OL,11,Fcost".
OL,13,FCritics have labelled the decision as
OL,14,Fthe most significant case of
OL,15,Fsportswashing in FIFA's history.
