OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FA recent report from HRW, titled "Die
OL,7,FFirst, and I'll Pay You Later," argues
OL,8,Fthat the Saudi government, headed by
OL,9,Fits de facto ruler Mohammed bin Salman
OL,10,F(MBS), is using the tournament to
OL,11,F"wash away its poor human rights
OL,12,Freputation".
OL,14,FAmnesty International said that the
OL,15,Fdecision "will put many lives at risk".
