OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,F"FIFA's reckless decision to award the
OL,7,F2034 World Cup to Saudi Arabia without
OL,8,Fensuring adequate human rights
OL,9,Fprotections are in place will put many
OL,10,Flives at risk," Amnesty's head of
OL,11,Flabour rights and sport Steve Cockburn
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe argument is also shared by Lina al-
OL,15,FHathloul, Head of Monitoring and
OL,16,FAdvocacy at ALQST for Human Rights,
OL,17,Fwho described the country as "a pure
OL,18,Fpolice state ruled by Crown Prince
OL,19,FMohammed bin Salman with no checks and
OL,20,Fbalances".
