OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FThe Saudis claim the country has made
OL,7,Fstrides in terms of human rights in
OL,8,Frecent years, but critics still say it
OL,9,Fhas a long way to go.
OL,11,FIn a 2023 interview with Fox News, MBS
OL,12,Fsaid he did not "care" if the
OL,13,Fcountry's investments were labelled as
OL,14,Fsportswashing, as long as they
OL,15,F"increase my GDP by one percent".
OL,17,FThis all raises the question of why
OL,18,FFIFA's decision to choose Saudi Arabia
OL,19,Fis so controversial, ITV News explains.
