OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FLGBTQ+ rights are virtually non-
OL,7,Fexistent in Saudi Arabia, and are not
OL,8,Flegally recognised or protected. The
OL,9,FSaudi government has previously
OL,10,Flabelled such suggestions as
OL,11,F"extremist ideas".
OL,13,FCurrently, Saudi Arabia's legal system
OL,14,Fbans LGBTQ+ relationships, public
OL,15,Fdisplays of affection, and gender
OL,16,Fexpression.
OL,18,FLGBTQ+ people face severe stigma,
OL,19,Fdiscrimination, and harsh penalties,
OL,20,Fincluding imprisonment, fines, or the
OL,21,Fdeath penalty, Amnesty says.
