OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FEqual rights
OL,8,FAmnesty claims that Saudi women remain
OL,9,Fsubject to discrimination in law and
OL,10,Fin practice.
OL,12,FThe organisation points to the
OL,13,Fcountry's male guardianship system -
OL,14,Fmade law in 2022 - which requires
OL,15,Fwomen to have a male legal guardian.
OL,16,FThey cannot choose who this guardian
OL,17,Fwill be.
OL,19,FHuman rights groups also claim that
OL,20,Fwomen could be subject to imprisonment
OL,21,Ffor violating Saudi practices and laws.
