OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FThis year, Manahel al-Otaibi was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 11 years in prison for
OL,8,Fusing social media to advocate against
OL,9,Frules requiring women to get a male
OL,10,Frelative's permission to marry or
OL,11,Ftravel.
OL,13,FIn 2023, Saudi Arabia carried out the
OL,14,Fthird-highest number of executions
OL,15,Fglobally, with 300 people having
OL,16,Falready been executed this year - a
OL,17,Frecord based on official figures.
OL,19,FThe country is also alleged to have
OL,20,Fcommitted executions on foreign soil.
