OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FMBS in 2018, according to US
OL,7,Fintelligence, approved an operation to
OL,8,Fcapture or kill journalist Jamal
OL,9,FKhashoggi, who was murdered and
OL,10,Fdismembered by Saudi agents inside the
OL,11,Fkingdom's consulate in Istanbul. He
OL,12,Fhas denied the allegations.
OL,14,FKhashoggi had been critical of the
OL,15,FSaudi government. His alleged
OL,16,Fassassination highlights the Saudi's
OL,17,Fcrackdown on the freedom of the press.
