OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FAmnesty reported that in 2022 Saudi
OL,7,Fauthorities arbitrarily detained
OL,8,FEthiopian men, women, and children for
OL,9,Fup to 18 months in "inhumane"
OL,10,Fconditions.
OL,12,FDetainees were said to be tortured,
OL,13,Fdenied adequate food, water,
OL,14,Fsanitation, and healthcare, and at
OL,15,Fleast 12 men died before their forced
OL,16,Fdeportation to Ethiopia.
OL,18,FTrials are reported to be unfair, with
OL,19,Flengthy prison sentences, solitary
OL,20,Fconfinement, and restricted
OL,21,Fcommunication.
