OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,FHRW said in a June statement that
OL,7,Femployees are "vulnerable to
OL,8,Fwidespread abuse, including contract
OL,9,Fsubstitution, exorbitant recruitment
OL,10,Ffees, non-payment of wages,
OL,11,Fconfiscation of passports by
OL,12,Femployers, and forced labour."
OL,14,FDespite a series of reforms announced
OL,15,Fby the Saudis in recent years,
OL,16,Femployers "still hold disproportionate
OL,17,Fcontrol over workers," HRW said.
OL,19,FAmnesty said there is "clear evidence"
OL,20,Fthat Fifa workers will be exploited.
