OL,3,CWhy Fifa awarding Saudi Arabia the
OL,4,C2034 World Cup is so controversial?
OL,6,F"Based on clear evidence to date, FIFA
OL,7,Fknows workers will be exploited and
OL,8,Feven die without fundamental reforms
OL,9,Fin Saudi Arabia, and yet has chosen to
OL,10,Fpress ahead regardless," Amnesty's
OL,11,FCockburn said.
OL,13,F"The organisation risks bearing a
OL,14,Fheavy responsibility for many of the
OL,15,Fhuman rights abuses that will follow."
